result.name: Tai Hing

reviews.text:
Good place for a afternoon lunch meal.

Typical hong kong 茶餐廳
Good service manner and good food
Came here and ordered Cantonese BBQ for lunch. I am impressed by the roasted goose. And the milk tea is always a delight.
We have order duck drumstick and dry beef noodle. Overall food is good, services so so..recommend for tourist

Good place for evening meal that is mid priced and decent quality, meals average around $120 HKD per person and you are able to eat family style. There's quite a bit of varied food choices here but the roast pork belly is stone cold and not enjoyable. Best roast product here is the goose which can be ordered as whole, half or quarter. Rice can be added on as well. Portions for any vegetables are very small and expensive for what you get given you can buy the vegetables inexpensively from any wet market, so very puzzling. Steam fish is fresh and not fishy old tasting, most meats come with dips. Free hot water available, and various drinks up for ordering as well. Cold red bean drink is better from other establishments as Tai Hing's variant is mostly milk and cream and very little red bean. Boiled chicken and soy chicken are very fresh and tasty as well. Sweet and sour pork basic (has too much gristle , so pork chop variant is probably better). Has a fair few tourists but mostly locals from what I saw. Queues often at peak times, for short table seating times get in earlier if you have time as once roasted food is used it isn't replenished throughout the night. Not everything in menu is available, some items never available regardless of time of day.

result.name: 太興

reviews.text: 長期排隊，門口總是自由行人士在收搭行李。上菜比較慢，可能人手缺，不能他們。太好生意。價錢不平大概一個晚餐連飲百幾
貴版茶餐廳，烧味質素每下愈况，價錢節節上升，伙記服務欠佳，如有其他選擇可以不去。
食物質素每況愈下，早、午餐價格偏高，師傅煎製荷包蛋技巧差劣(蛋黄蛋白渾為一體，老人家不宜吃蛋黄，你叫人怎樣分開黄、白呢？大家樂做得最漂亮)。同樣，太陽蛋亦是冰冷的。可幸員工服務態度很好！
